iven? Verses 4, 5. </div><div class="t m1d0 x71 h4 yb8d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1ef3 x74 h4 yd2e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What warning is given the church concerning aposta-</div><div class="t m21e0 x5f h4 y5ac ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sies? 2 Thess. 2: 3; Acts 20: 29, 30. </div><div class="t m1d2 x26 h4 y941 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m4b9 x74 h4 yd68 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How was the first period of the early church typified in </div><div class="t mb1f xc h4 yeed ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a subsequent vision given the revelator? Rev. 6: 1, 2. </div><div class="t m229 xc h4 ye82 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Note 4. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
